  "2026-07-23T05:33:55.569Z",claude-code-agent,"Fresh health evidence 2026-07-23: pm health --check-only reports storage warn with 167 unknown-author events, partitioned into 162 legacy and 5 actionable across 1,925 streams / 32,373 checked events. This is the existing canonical item; no duplicate was created and it was not claimed by the truthful-context PR."
  "2026-07-24T06:14:19.250Z",claude-code-agent,"Evidence 2026-07-24: shipped opt-in strict mutation authorship, explicit TestAllCommandOptions.author parity, and append-only history:author-acknowledge disposition. Reviewed and acknowledged the five exact post-baseline test_run_track events as codex-wide-sdk-20260716 without rewriting immutable streams. Live pm health now reports 167 total unknown events = 162 legacy + 5 acknowledged, 0 actionable, overall ok:true; validate reports 0 history drift. Linked tests passed. Full repository coverage passed 6208 tests at exact 100% statements/branches/functions/lines; lint, typecheck, docs links, contracts, security, and packed-install acceptance passed."
